* Tue Mar 14 2006 Vladimir Sokolovsky <vlad@mellanox.co.il>
- Added ibdiagpath utility
* Wed Jan 18 2006 Vladimir Sokolovsky <vlad@mellanox.co.il>
- Initial packaging for gen2 stack
